{"tid":2402974,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"蜘蛛俠3｜湯賀蘭親口否認三代同堂　「不過Marvel唔係首次呃我」","createTime":"2021-02-10T21:02:05.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-11T14:53:01.000Z","uid":130626,"like":90,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":48,"replies":[{"pid":"c19c4caa869b75f09a98a07d5bb25d35e270a4cb","tid":2402974,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T21:02:05.000Z","msg":"Marvel聯合SONY PICTURE合製的超級英雄電影《蜘蛛俠3》（Spider-Man），一直以來都有傳會有不少舊角色回歸，大玩平行宇宙，目前確定了反派「電魔」占美霍士（Jamie Foxx）和「八爪魚博士」艾佛莫連納（Alfred Molina）將會加入，而「奇異博士」班尼狄甘巴貝治（Benedict Cumberbatch）則會成為蜘蛛俠的人生導師。<br />\n<br />\n早前一直有傳Marvel和SONY會搵來三代蜘蛛俠同台，令影迷對於杜比麥奎爾（Tobey Maguire）、安德魯加菲（Andrew Garfield）以及湯賀蘭（Tom Holland）同場的期待值極高。加上在最近一集《WandaVision》中，「紅女巫」伊莉莎白奧森（Elizabeth Olsen）重新安排角色，由變種特攻（X-MEN）的「快銀」Peter Evans飾演自己的弟弟，由此打開了首個平行宇宙，影集更會連接到《奇異博士2》（Doctor Strange in the Multiverse of Madness）的瘋狂多元宇宙，令到影迷更加相信《蜘蛛俠3》都會有同樣做法，將盛傳的舊角通通帶到《蜘蛛俠3》當中。<br />\n<br />\n不過近日湯賀蘭向外媒正式回應三代同堂的問題，他：「不，不，他們不會出現在這部電影中，除非他們向我隱瞞這重大的信息，對我來說這是天大的秘密，據我目前所知，他們不會出現。」究竟Marvel係又爆湯賀蘭爆響口劇透還是人係冇三代同堂呢？<br />\n<br />\n事實上，Marvel已經唔係第一次呃湯賀蘭，影迷應該記得在《復仇者聯盟4：終局之戰》（Avengers: Endgame）中，最後鐵甲奇俠羅拔唐尼的喪禮中，他曾被告知他要參加的是結婚派對，雖然當時他覺得大家面露哀傷的表情感到奇怪，湯賀蘭在訪問中同樣有提起此事更自嘲：「我100%肯定他們會繼續整蠱我，其實我已經拍了8星期，不過我還是對於這套電影毫無頭緒。」究竟Marvel係又爆湯賀蘭爆響口劇透還是真係冇三代同堂呢？<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210210/436201656065986560096721.jpeg/vuojqfj0UGBTRa5CLQP6g8guOuD2o4aWEVrDgxFaw4M?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210210%2F436201656065986560096721.jpeg%2Fvuojqfj0UGBTRa5CLQP6g8guOuD2o4aWEVrDgxFaw4M%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=cd30f098&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210210/436143995333120000930268.jpeg/bLpU8TwWLPsakp7A5RS-RsZRWaNe63OwQYZdFEGGXRQ?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210210%2F436143995333120000930268.jpeg%2FbLpU8TwWLPsakp7A5RS-RsZRWaNe63OwQYZdFEGGXRQ%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=dfcc16c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nMarvel曾呃湯賀蘭，羅拔唐尼的喪禮是婚禮。（《復仇者聯盟4：終局之戰》電影劇照）"},{"pid":"f8a81873b0afb8ec9d791a6d3c1d3a50bdc63988","tid":2402974,"uid":96704,"like":129,"dislike":0,"score":129,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T21:15:23.000Z","msg":"01真係垃撚圾<br />\n人地叫Evan Peters呀"},{"pid":"e26cff51d98b8af65a19f33154f2fa768712a290","tid":2402974,"uid":263534,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f8a81873b0afb8ec9d791a6d3c1d3a50bdc63988","tid":2402974,"uid":96704,"like":129,"dislike":0,"score":129,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T21:15:23.000Z","msg":"01真係垃撚圾<br />\n人地叫Evan Peters呀"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T23:06:13.000Z","msg":"仲有人哋係孖生大佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c8d06a79ab69bc87ec84c61b494e5f53f9c7eba","tid":2402974,"uid":19725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e26cff51d98b8af65a19f33154f2fa768712a290","tid":2402974,"uid":263534,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f8a81873b0afb8ec9d791a6d3c1d3a50bdc63988","tid":2402974,"uid":96704,"like":129,"dislike":0,"score":129,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T21:15:23.000Z","msg":"01真係垃撚圾<br />\n人地叫Evan Peters呀"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T23:06:13.000Z","msg":"仲有人哋係孖生大佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T00:01:01.000Z","msg":"呢個quicksilver 輕鬆打死thanos la <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd54306a8b2d78c35c7ddac768b7c3de1b31e9a6","tid":2402974,"uid":112416,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T00:07:07.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"purple\">班尼狄甘巴貝治</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"bacefd0011aaffc750095d7b1523162f979a8310","tid":2402974,"uid":112416,"like":2,"dislike":19,"score":-17,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T00:11:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210210/436143995333120000930268.jpeg/bLpU8TwWLPsakp7A5R